sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant DESC as Descope
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant AUTH as Auth Middleware
    participant API as FastAPI Routes
    participant DB as Aurora (PostgreSQL)

    U->>FE: Visit app
    FE->>DESC: Initialize Descope SDK
    U->>DESC: Login (email/SSO)
    DESC-->>FE: JWT (access token + refresh token)
    FE->>FE: Store token in memory

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over FE,API: Authenticated API Request
        FE->>APIGW: GET /api/regulations<br/>Authorization: Bearer {JWT}
        APIGW->>AUTH: Forward request
        AUTH->>DESC: Validate JWT (JWKS)
        DESC-->>AUTH: Token valid + claims
        AUTH->>AUTH: Extract role, tenant_id, user_id
        AUTH->>AUTH: Check role permissions
        alt Role Authorized
            AUTH->>API: Inject CurrentUser into request
            API->>DB: Query with tenant isolation
            DB-->>API: Results
            API-->>FE: 200 JSON response
        else Role Denied
            AUTH-->>FE: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over FE,AUTH: Public Endpoints (No Auth)
        FE->>APIGW: GET /health
        APIGW->>AUTH: Forward request
        AUTH->>AUTH: Path in PUBLIC_PATHS - skip auth
        AUTH->>API: Pass through
        API-->>FE: 200 healthy
    end
